g.text: WAL segment switches occur when one of the following events happens:
1. WAL segment is filled up (max WAL segmemt size is 16 Mb by default)
3. is enabled and the time set
When a WAL segment file is switched, it is usually recycled (renamed and reused) for future use.
However, it may be removed later if it is not needed.
WAL 0 has been renamed to WAL7
